= Action name = PCK.AUTOMIC_TENABLE_IO.PUB.ACTION.DOWNLOAD_SCAN_RESULTS
= General Description = This action exports the scan result for provided scan id.
= Failure Conditions = * If retry count reaches to the provided count and result is not fetched.
= Inputs = - Scan ID *: Provide the ID of the scan to get its results. E.g. 42 - Chapters: Specify chapters to include in the export in a semi-colon delimited string as a combination of the options: vuln_hosts_summary, vuln_by_host, compliance_exec, remediations, vuln_by_plugin, compliance. - Asset ID*: The ID of the asset scanned. E.g. f56168ed-b719-4273-b58c-a340a09ffbce - Format: Provide UUID for the editor template to use. E.g. csv - File: Provide a file name with the full path to download. E.g. C:\Automic\Automation.Platform\Agents\rapidautomation\WEBSERVICEREST01\bin\..\temp\log-0001311058.txt - Initial Waiting Time (in min): Provide initial waiting time. E.g. 2 - Retry Count: Provide the number of retry attempts to get the status.E.g. 5 - Retry Interval (in sec): Provide the interval in seconds between retry attempt.E.g. 60
= Behavior = * Action fails if an incorrect path is provided for File field. * If the user does not provide any path in File field, A file will be created in WEBSERVICEREST working directory with name log-[Action run id]. * If the user only provides the file name then the file will be created under the WEBSERVICEREST working directory. * If the file is already existing with the same name, action will overwrite it.
= Implementation Guide = * Action uses 3 jobs for downloading result. The first job will prepare a file, the second job will check if the file is ready to be downloaded and third for which downloads the file. Timeout parameters are used to check if the file is ready to be downloaded or not i.e. Second job in action.
= Return Value = - UC4RB_TIO_SAVED_LOG_FILE_PATH#: File path where the file is saved.
= Logging = AE logs will be displayed in the AE report.
= Rollback = (none)
= Example = - Scan ID*: 42 - Chapters : vuln_hosts_summary - Asset ID*: f56168ed-b719-4273-b58c-a340a09ffbce - Format* : csv - File : C:\automic\log-scan-report.csv - Initial Waiting Time (in min) : 1 - Retry Count : 3 - Retry Interval (in sec) : 30
